cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with deep generative models and their application to multimodal data, specifically images and text. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses downstream tasks such as compositionality and visual relation prediction, which further supports the likelihood of it belonging to these sub-categories.
